<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#5865f2">
    <title>QuestCord - Under Maintenance</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@700;900&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated background gradient */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(10, 10, 26, 0.95) 0%, rgba(26, 10, 62, 0.9) 50%, rgba(15, 31, 62, 0.95) 100%);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientShift 20s ease infinite;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Nebula effect */
        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.2) 0%, transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.25) 0%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 80%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 60% 20%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) 0%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 50%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, transparent 25%);
            animation: rotateNebula 40s linear infinite;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        }

        @keyframes rotateNebula {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1); }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .icon-container {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.8));
        }

        .gear-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 8px solid #5865f2;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: relative;
            animation: spin 4s linear infinite;
        }

        .gear-icon::before,
        .gear-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: #5865f2;
        }

        .gear-icon::before {
            width: 30px;
            height: 60px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .gear-icon::after {
            width: 60px;
            height: 30px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5865f2 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 1.8rem);
            color: #b9bbbe;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
            color: #b9bbbe;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .status-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .status-indicator {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background: #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.8);
        }

        .status-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fbbf24;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .discord-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5865f2 0%, #4752c4 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
        }

        .discord-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.6);
        }

        .features-list {
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .features-list li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #b9bbbe;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .features-list li::before {
            content: '⚙️';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .gear-icon {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .status-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .discord-link {
                padding: 12px 30px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <div class="gear-icon"></div>
        </div>

        <h1>Under Maintenance</h1>
        <h2>We'll be back soon!</h2>

        <div class="status-box">
            <div class="status-indicator">
                <span class="status-dot"></span>
                <span class="status-text">Maintenance in Progress</span>
            </div>
            <p class="info-text">We're currently performing scheduled maintenance to improve your experience.</p>
        </div>

        <p>
            Our team is working hard to bring you the best QuestCord experience possible.
            We're making improvements to our systems and will be back online shortly.
        </p>

        <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
                <li>Database optimizations</li>
                <li>Performance improvements</li>
                <li>New features and bug fixes</li>
                <li>Enhanced security measures</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>
            Thank you for your patience! The Discord bot is still operational,
            so you can continue your quests while we work on the website.
        </p>

        <a href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<%= process.env.DISCORD_CLIENT_ID %>&permissions=2048&scope=bot%20applications.commands" class="discord-link" target="_blank">
            Add to Discord
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
